OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FThames Water has confirmed an improved
OL,7,Frescue bid has been tabled by
OL,8,Fcreditors for the troubled supplier
OL,9,Fbut said talks are ongoing over the
OL,10,Fproposals.
OL,12,FBritain's biggest water supplier,
OL,13,Fwhich has around 16 million customers,
OL,14,Fsaid bidding consortium London &
OL,15,FValley Water (L&VW) has put forward
OL,16,Fplans to inject #3.35 billion of new
OL,17,Fequity and up to #6.55 billion in new
OL,18,Fdebt as it looks to secure backing for
OL,19,Fits deal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
