PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FThe planned bid ` which was first
OL,7,Freported over the weekend ` marks an
OL,8,Fincrease from the offer lodged in
OL,9,FOctober last year by the consortium of
OL,10,FThames Water's main creditors,
OL,11,Fincluding institutional investors such
OL,12,Fas Aberdeen, Elliott Management and
OL,13,FSilverpoint Capital.
OL,15,FThames Water said the proposal
OL,16,F"remains subject to ongoing review by
OL,17,Fthe company, Ofwat and other
OL,18,Fregulators, and subject to discussion
OL,19,Fwith the company's financial
OL,20,Fstakeholders".
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
