PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FIt added: "As engagement remains
OL,7,Fongoing, there is no certainty that
OL,8,Fthe L&VW Proposal will be accepted or
OL,9,Fthat it will be finalised in its
OL,10,Fcurrent form.
OL,12,F"At this stage, the company's board,
OL,13,FOfwat, other regulators and relevant
OL,14,Finvestment committees have made no
OL,15,Fdecision to accept and take forward
OL,16,Fthe L&VW proposal to implementation."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@eO]
