PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FThames Water is hoping to secure the
OL,7,Fdeal to stave off temporary
OL,8,Fnationalisation after being left on
OL,9,Fthe brink of collapse by nearly #20
OL,10,Fbillion of debt.
OL,12,FA rescue bid by creditors is seen as
OL,13,Fthe final realistic option on the
OL,14,Ftable to avoid being placed into the
OL,15,FGovernment's special administration
OL,16,Fregime after a previous rescue deal
OL,17,Fwith US private equity giant KKR
OL,18,Fcollapsed in May.
OL,20,FAdministrators have already been lined
OL,21,Fup to step in if needed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
