FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FAs well as an equity and debt
OL,7,Finjection, the bid proposal includes
OL,8,Fcommitments from the creditors not to
OL,9,Fsell a significant proportion of
OL,10,Ftheir equity investment over the
OL,11,Fregulatory cycle through to 2030, and
OL,12,Falso prevents Thames Water from
OL,13,Fpaying dividends to shareholders
OL,14,Fbefore April 2035.
OL,16,FIt could only start to pay dividends
OL,17,Fbefore this date if it becomes a
OL,18,Flisted company, it said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
