OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773655496
OL,3,CThames Water creditors pledge #3.4bn
OL,4,Cof new equity in improved rescue bid
OL,6,FThe revised offer would also see the
OL,7,Fcreditors accept up to 30% of the
OL,8,Fcompany's debt load being written off
OL,9,Fto help reduce the water firm's vast
OL,10,Fdebt mountain.
OL,12,FIts creditors are the bondholders who
OL,13,Fnow effectively own Thames Water after
OL,14,Fthe High Court approved a financial
OL,15,Frestructuring earlier this year
OL,16,Fthrough a loan of up to #3 billion to
OL,17,Fensure it can keep running until the
OL,18,Fsummer of 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
